text: "Headline News" is a song by "Weird Al" Yankovic. It is a parody of the Crash Test Dummies's song "Mmm Mmm Mmm Mmm". It describes current events at the time in a humorous way. It was released on the 1994 album Permanent Record: Al in the Box. Category:"Weird Al" Yankovic songs Category:Parodies Category:1994 songs
title: Headline News ("Weird Al" Yankovic song)
